citation: Proclamation under the Health Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2022 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Health Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2022

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Health Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act 2022 fix 24 October 2022 as the day on which the provisions of that Act commence.

24 October 2022

B. BAKER

Governor

By Her Excellency's Command,

JEREMY ROCKLIFF

Minister for Health

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 24 October 2022

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Health.
